{"name":"glowworm","size":"small","type":"monstrosity","tag":"","alignment":"unaligned","hitDice":"2","armorName":"none","shieldBonus":0,"natArmorBonus":1,"otherArmorDesc":"11 (natural armor)","speed":"10","burrowSpeed":"0","climbSpeed":"30","flySpeed":"0","hover":false,"swimSpeed":"0","customHP":false,"customSpeed":false,"hpText":"18 (4d6 + 4)","speedDesc":"20 ft.","strPoints":"16","dexPoints":"12","conPoints":"13","intPoints":"2","wisPoints":"10","chaPoints":"5","blindsight":"60","blind":false,"darkvision":"0","tremorsense":"0","truesight":"0","telepathy":0,"cr":"1/2","customCr":"1/4 (50 XP)","customProf":2,"isLegendary":false,"legendariesDescription":"The dretch can take 3 legendary actions, choosing from the options below. Only one legendary action option can be used at a time and only at the end of another creature's turn. The dretch regains spent legendary actions at the start of its turn.","isLair":false,"lairDescription":"When fighting inside its lair, the dretch can invoke the ambient magic to take lair actions. On initiative count 20 (losing initiative ties), the dretch can take one lair action to cause one of the following effects:","lairDescriptionEnd":"The dretch can't repeat an effect until they have all been used, and it can't use the same effect two rounds in a row.","isMythic":false,"mythicDescription":"If the dretch's mythic trait is active, it can use the options below as legendary actions for 1 hour after using {Some Ability}.","isRegional":false,"regionalDescription":"The region containing the dretch's lair is warped by the creature's presence, which creates one or more of the following effects:","regionalDescriptionEnd":"If the dretch dies, the first two effects fade over the course of 3d10 days.","properties":[],"abilities":[{"name":"Glowing Lure","desc":"A creature which looks at the [MON]'s lure must make a DC 13 Wisdom saving throw. A creature which fails two of these in a row is stunned for one round. A creature can look away from a lure, but they are considered blinded if they attempt to attack the [MON]."},{"name":"Mucus Coat","desc":"While on the ceiling, the [MON] is hidden and protected by mucus. It can be perceived with a DC 13 perception check and is resistant to piercing damage."}],"actions":[{"name":"Descending Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [1d12 + 1] piercing damage. The [MON] can drop up to 60ft through a strand of mucus from the ceiling to bite a target."},{"name":"Bite","desc":"_Melee Weapon Attack:_ [STR ATK] to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. _Hit:_ [1d4 + 1] piercing damage."}],"bonusActions":[],"reactions":[],"legendaries":[],"mythics":[],"lairs":[],"regionals":[],"sthrows":[],"skills":[{"name":"stealth","stat":"dex"}],"damagetypes":[],"specialdamage":[],"conditions":[],"languages":[],"understandsBut":"","shortName":"","pluralName":"","doubleColumns":false,"separationPoint":0,"damage":[]}